{"tid":2240825,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"潘焯鴻：掛8號係人治決定 仲要掛足全日","createTime":"2020-10-13T02:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T09:00:49.000Z","uid":210495,"like":10,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"02c8324d5bd98e15021618d9844faafa61951ebc","tid":2240825,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T02:51:08.000Z","msg":"記憶中﹐過往天文台非常不願掛8號風球。<br />\n<br />\n其中一個8號的標準﹐除了要風大雨大外﹐還要香港有3個風站或以上﹐其中一個要是市區內﹐風力持續達65km/hr的烈風標準以上。<br />\n<br />\n現在﹐無論持續或陣風都根本不達8號風球所需的烈風標準。港內即市區的青洲風站持續及陣風都分別是48及63公里﹐達不到65km/hr的烈風水平。 <br />\n<br />\n一個450km外的風暴浪卡﹐而且路徑明顯不會趨近香港﹐沒有烈風數據支持﹐掛8號令人難免覺得是人治的決定﹐而非地球物理氣象引起的防禦需要。<br />\n<br />\n希望見到林超英等退休天文專業為大家分析一下掛8號風球的程序公義。<br />\n<br />\np.s. 有說季候風影響增強風力﹐因而足以掛8號風球﹐我對這說法不敢認同。<br />\n<br />\n#咁就8號風球<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/104317187641943/posts/399873141419678/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F104317187641943%2Fposts%2F399873141419678%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2VyQscPELFEQk1IFn5y5IyWs%3D&h=579624cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/104317187641943/posts/399873141419678/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"c0a1a3e3c232e2760b0759003e0fede44c218262","tid":2240825,"uid":361751,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T02:51:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBQeXTs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBQeXTs.jpg&h=def0aea7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06abd082d676d0ed7c6c12777360afbb95a1aaa8","tid":2240825,"uid":62226,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T02:52:48.000Z","msg":"做開老闆先會諗呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b354e62cda8137f88f198a36896a541166ef08f","tid":2240825,"uid":199670,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T02:54:14.000Z","msg":"On9 條友唔識扮專家"},{"pid":"7b7dd973040b9d2df60acdc761127caf47e004bd","tid":2240825,